WEBVTT

21:55.720 --> 21:58.490 line:80%
The people's surplus grain is not enough
to fill their own stomachs.

21:58.490 --> 21:59.960 line:80%
Levying grain locally?

22:00.280 --> 22:01.410 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei,

22:01.720 --> 22:03.360 line:80%
are you not worried

22:03.830 --> 22:05.890 line:80%
that it will incite a civil uprising?
